[<p>\u201cTo all Latinos in the United States of America: We cannot allow them to insult and abuse us anymore,\u201d the 50-year-old \xa0Mexican-American actress <a href="/web/20161007073458/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wy2Eai0NHLk&amp;list=PLt9jO9QkAAoeXUt-4UEzw0fuDrEUu4f01&amp;index=29" target="_blank">said</a>\xa0in the Spanish-language ad released by the Clinton campaign Thursday.</p>, <p>Hayek says Latinos can show GOP presidential nominee Donald Trump and the rest of America that there is a \u201cmighty community\u201d of active Latino voters.</p>, <p>\u201cThe Latino vote is extremely important.\xa0We can prove that we are a mighty community.\xa0We have to vote.\xa0Vote for Hillary Clinton,\u201d the\xa0<em>Sausage Party\xa0</em>star said in the ad. \u201cAlso, those of us who can vote owe it to the undocumented immigrants who don\u2019t have a voice.\u201d</p>, <p><iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="557" src="/web/20161007073458if_/https://www.youtube.com/embed/wy2Eai0NHLk?feature=oembed" width="990"></iframe></p>, <p>An outspoken supporter of Clinton, Hayek said in April that Clinton is the \u201c<a href="/web/20161007073458/http://www.breitbart.com/big-hollywood/2016/04/20/salma-hayek-hillary-clinton-is-the-only-candidate-who-can-lead-the-fight-against-isis/" target="_blank">only person</a>\u201d who can lead the fight against ISIS.</p>, <p>A constant critic of Republican candidate Donald Trump, the Oscar-nominated actress recently offered to lend Trump a copy of\xa0<em>U.S. History for Dummies.\xa0</em></p>, <p>\u201cMr. Trump, I recommend to you to read this book,\u201d <a href="/web/20161007073458/http://www.breitbart.com/big-hollywood/2016/08/04/salma-hayek-offers-donald-trump-u-s-history-dummies-will-gladly-lend-copy/" target="_blank">Hayek\xa0said</a> during an August appearance on <i>The Late Late Show With James Corden. \u201c</i>I will gladly lend you my copy,\u201d she added\xa0while holding up a copy of the book.</p>, <p>\xa0</p>, <p><em>Follow\xa0<a href="/web/20161007073458/https://twitter.com/jeromeehudson" target="_blank">Jerome Hudson</a>\xa0on Twitter\xa0<a href="/web/20161007073458/https://twitter.com/jeromeehudson" target="_blank">@jeromeehudson</a></em></p>]